Game Controller Emulation Server

This server servers browser pages that allow for the emulations of
game pads on the local machine that is running the server.


INSTALLATION

first download and install vJoy from http://vjoystick.sourceforge.net/site/index.php/download-a-install/download

then, download the SDK from https://github.com/shauleiz/vJoy/tree/master/SDK

copy the lib/vJoyInterface.dll file into the root of the pyvjoy module folder (lib/amd64/vJoyInterface.dll if you are using 64-bit Python)

pip install flask
